query:
SELECT 
  pwi.id as wave_item_id,
  pwi.productName,
  pwi.pickingOrderId,
  po.id as order_id,
  po.customerOrderNumber
FROM pickingWaveItems pwi
LEFT JOIN pickingOrders po ON pwi.pickingOrderId = po.id
WHERE pwi.id IN (30015, 30016, 30017, 30018, 30019);
